metadata.name: ZIELCHAIN SOUL NAT3
metadata.description: ZIELCHAIN is an NFT project that aims to create new IP in collaboration with the community, based on the concept arts and character arts created by the globally renowned illustrator Yoshitaka Amano. ZIELCHAIN SOUL NAT3 Collection is available exclusively at NFT ART TOKYO3, held in Shibuya, Tokyo on June 3, 2023. ZIELCHAIN SOUL NAT3 holders are able to mint the main ZIELCHAIN collection for free once the minting process is available. â€» ZIELCHAIN SOUL NAT3 is non-transferable (SBT) until the main ZIELCHAIN collection minting process is available.
